    BuildPhaseStart((Build Phase)) --> SpawnBuildAgent[Spawn orchestration-build Agent]
    SpawnBuildAgent --> BuildLoop_Start

    subgraph BuildLoop_SG ["Build-Test-Fix Loop"]
        BuildLoop_Start[Implement Fixes] --> BuildP1[P1: Investigation]
        BuildP1 --> BuildP2[P2: Fix Global Flags Regression]
        BuildP2 --> BuildP3[P3: Fix Phase-Qualified Task IDs]
        BuildP3 --> BuildP4[P4: Documentation Updates]
        BuildP4 --> BuildLoop_End
    end

    BuildLoop_End --> TestPhaseStart

    %% Test Phase
    TestPhaseStart((Test Phase)) --> SpawnTestAgent[Spawn orchestration-test Agent]
    SpawnTestAgent --> TestLoop_Start

    subgraph TestLoop_SG ["Test-Fix Loop"]
        TestLoop_Start[Run Validation] --> TestP1[P1: Global Flags Validation]
